results.title: The Rawhide Kid (2010) #2
results.description:
“TOMBSTONE BLUES,” PART 2
The sharpest-dressed sharpshooter in Wild West is back in the saddle again – and this time he’s not riding alone!  When Wyatt and Morgan Earp are taken hostage by Cristo Pike and his pack of pistoleros, the Rawhide Kid must put together a posse of the greatest western heroes in the Marvel Universe to rescue the Earp brothers and bring Pike to justice: Kid Colt, Doc Holliday, Annie Oakley, Billy the Kid, Red Wolf and The Two-Gun Kid!  But before the Sensational Seven faces its High Noon showdown, it’s got to get there in one piece – which ain’t easy considering this posses’ complicated history.
Parental Advisory …$3.99

results.title: House of M (2005) #6
results.description: Both the Avengers and X-Men have come to realize the truth about the House of M, and they cannot let it stand! With the power of S.H.I.E.L.D behind them, their plan is to assault Magneto when he would least expect it: at a gala event held in his honor on his island kingdom of Genosha. The stakes have never been higher, and the heroes will stop at nothing to ensure that the Scarlet Witch returns the world to what it what it once was!

results.title: SPIDER-MAN VS. VAMPIRES (2010) #2
results.description:
MARVEL DIGITAL COMICS EXCLUSIVE
VAMPIRES!  You can't trust them, even when they're on your side. From the pages of Marvel Digital, Spider-Man's had a long history with Blade, the Vampire hunter, but when he finds him enslaved in an underground, undead fighting league, the web-head must fight Blade for his very life or face the curse of the Vampire! Kevin Grevioux (ADAM: LEGEND OF THE BLUE MARVEL) and Roberto Castro (NEW EXILES) bring you all the bloodsucking action!
